  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 3 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A 3-year-old child died after falling into the fish tank",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said a 3-year-old child fell into a fish tank and died in the Madukele area under the Panvila police division.",
        "The baby died after falling into a 20-foot-deep water tank used to raise fish in front of the house.",
        "While the baby and mother were at home, the baby who was playing alone in front of the house fell into the fish tank."
      ],
